## 5. Circuit Connection Diagram (Pin Mapping)

### 5.1 ACS712 Current Sensor to ESP32
* **VCC** ➡️ ESP32 **5V / VIN**
* **GND** ➡️ ESP32 **GND**
* **OUT (Analog Out)** ➡️ ESP32 **GPIO 34** (Analog Input Pin)

### 5.2 5V Relay Module to ESP32
* **VCC** ➡️ ESP32 **5V / VIN**
* **GND** ➡️ ESP32 **GND**
* **IN (Signal Pin)** ➡️ ESP32 **GPIO 25**

### 5.3 Power Line Connections
* Connect the **Live AC Wire** from your main power supply to the **Common (COM)** terminal of the relay.
* Connect the **Normally Open (NO)** terminal of the relay to one terminal of the **ACS712 current sensor terminal block**.
* Connect the other terminal of the **ACS712 block** directly to your **EV Charger input**.

